H. No. 499 / 67 OG No. 36, 7040 (September 6, 1971)

[ REPUBLIC ACT NO. 6193, June 19, 1971 ]

AN ACT CREATING CERTAIN BARRIOS IN THE MUNICIPALITY OF VILLABA, PROVINCE OF

LEYTE.

Be it enacted, by the Senate and House of Representatives of the Philippines

in Congress assembled:

SECTION 1. The following sitios in the Municipality of Villaba, Province of Leyte, are hereby converted into barrios, of said municipality, to wit:

Sitio Tabunoc, to be known as Barrio Tabunoc;

Sitio Hibulangan, to be known as Barrio Hibulangan;

Sitio Camporog, to be known as Barrio Camporog;

Sitio Payao, to be known as Barrio Payao;

Sitio Cabungahan, to be known as Barrio Cabungahan;

Sitio Tinghob, to be known as Barrio Tinghob;

Sitio Catagbacan, to be known as Barrio Gatagbacan;

Sitio Halas, to be known as Barrio Halas;

Sitio Fatima, to be known as Barrio Fatima;

Sitio Iligay, to be known as Barrio Iligay;

Sitio Baga-Buga to be known as Barrio Baga-Buga;

Sitio Capinyahan, to be known as Barrio Capinyahan;

Sitio Poblacion Norte, to be known as Barrio Poblacion Norte; and

Sitio Poblaeion Sur, to be known as Barrio Poblacion Sur.
